| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0219 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 05190c5b-115a-52a2-a52f-de1cbb2ee0f4"
